dia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"17-year-old gymnast\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"Nedoroscik\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"glasses\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the pommel horse\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's hilarious.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the attention he's getting - I think he deserves it,\\\" Tung said.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"Tung\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung, who started gymnastics at 5 years old, began following Nedoroscik's Olympic journey about a year ago.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tung\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"Nedoroscik's Olympic journey\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I was competing.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like Stephen,\\\" the Rancho Santa Margarita teen added.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stephen\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rancho Santa Margarita teen\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The similarities do not stop with the sport and the spectacles: Tung is also a Rubik's Cube enthusiast like his pommel horse hero.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The similarities\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacles\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"Tung\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"a Rubik's Cube enthusiast\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"his pommel horse hero\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says this helps him with the analytical part of gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the analytical part\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just love all the ways you can analyze your routines and almost every single detail in your training comes into not only your daily life - but your routine in general,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the ways\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"your routines\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"almost every single detail\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"your training\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"not only your daily life\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"your routine\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung says he just started wearing contacts while competing a few weeks ago, so he's used to depending on his sense of touch.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tung\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"contacts\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"his sense\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nedoroscik has described doing the same.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nedoroscik\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung added that he's also been inspired by other Olympians, like Brazilian gold medalist Rebeca Andrade, who has to put on her glasses to see the scoreboard.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.